quote.summary: Honliv Healthcare Management Group Co Ltd is an investment holding company principally engaged in the ownership, operation and management of hospitals. The Company, together with its subsidiaries, mainly provides treatment and general healthcare services and pharmaceutical sales. The Company's outpatient pharmaceutical treatment fields include the outpatient department, paediatrics, emergency department, haematology, obstetrics and gynaecology, dermatology, neurology, nails and breasts and preventive healthcare. The Company also engages in the provision of treatments and general healthcare services, including the sales of medical consumables and the provision of hospital ancillary services, and the sales of pharmaceuticals to patients, including both inpatients and outpatients. The Company mainly conducts its businesses in the domestic market and overseas markets.
